/** 
\defgroup IfxLld_Demo_DmaBasicDemo Dma basic Memory to memory transfer Demo
\ingroup IfxLld_Demo


\par Introduction
This application demo show how to use the Dma for basic memory to memory transfers
It features the following:
- Initialisation of Dma for Memory to Memory transfers
- Trigger Dma to Transfer Data (16 words) from Source Buffer to Destination Buffer using the \ref IfxLld_Dma_Dma API 
- Verify the data transfers by comparing source and destination buffers

\par Hardware used
Uses the Dma

\par Tested on
This demo application has been tested on the TC27xB device with the iLLD version 1.0.0.0 using a triboard.


